                    <span>A good attempt at explaining the costs of living in capitalism. A bit dated considering the World Trade Organization, computerization and downsizing, but he makes points most people need to hear and consider. Well worth reading and thinking about. Order a copy and begin to think!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A fantastic and important book</div>
